            <h2 id="General">General Rules</h2>
            <p>We will follow RGL bans up to this point. If you would like to appeal your ban submit a ticket on the discord.</p>
            <h4 id="cheating">1.1 Cheating</h4>
            <p>First offense: 2 year ban</p>
            <p>Second offense: permanent</p>
            <h2 id="1v1-rules">1v1 Rules</h2>
            <h4 id="general-1v1">2.1 General</h4>
            <p>1.1 Class restrictions: 2 scouts, 2 soldiers, 1 demo per team</p>
            <p>1.2 One class swap per player per match. This means each team member on a team can switch one time each.</p>
            <p>1.3 Every match must be demo recorded.</p>
            <p>1.4 Whitelist is 'whitelist.tf/14451'</p>
            <h4 id="matches-1v1">2.2 Matches</h4>
            <p>2.1 Matches for the regular season will be Best of 5</p>
            <p>2.2 Matches can be played on a public MGE server or a private server</p>
            <p>2.3 Match scores must be reported in Match Comms</p>
            <p>2.4 Default match times are Saturday 8:30pm EST. Matches must be played within 1 week of the default match time.</p>
